  "metadata": {
    "template": true,
    "description": "Prove Blacknode moves a real SO-ARM101 (6x Feetech STS3215 servos) end to end: discover the USB serial port, launch the Feetech bus driver, preflight and read the live pose over native rclpy, then set Native Set Joint armed=true to move one joint. Safe by default: armed is off, and the driver seeds each servo's Goal_Position from its current reading before enabling torque so nothing snaps when it starts.",
    "color": "#14b8a6",
    "required_packages": ["blacknode-robot", "blacknode-ros2"]
  },
